data.description: **ASSUME LOW INTEREST RATE (2.99%) ON THIS LOVELY 4 BEDROOM HOME WITH PRIMARY BEDROOM DOWN**3 large bedrooms up (all have large walk-in closets) has been totally updated in 2022 with new cabinets (gorgeous custom color in kitchen), back slider door, dishwasher and even upgraded ss refrigerator, recessed lighting in kitchen, toilet and bathroom flooring; plus water heater and outside HVAC compressor.  Primary bath down has walk in shower.   Huge gameroom upstairs.  Roof replaced on 2021. So much to offer in this lovely home and in a convenient area close to Lackland, Kelly and less than 20 min. to downtown.  Please verify schools.  Also, offering VA assumption to buyer who is able to pay seller's equity and assume 2.99% existing on existing loan - with qualifying with existing lender.
